There is an actual legit way to get out of duct tape if the need ever arised.
1. If you can, stand up, if not, try to kneel down so your knee is sticking out in front of you.
2. Hold your knee up if your standing, if you aren't, just proceed with step 3
3. Bring your hands up above your head and then forcefully bring them down over your knee, so your knee goes between your wrists
4. The duct tape should rip, if not try again until it does.
This actually works! It may take a few tries but it will work eventually!

Also if you have duct tape over your mouth, it may seem silly, but just lick around your lips and try to bite at it>
